steps.prompt:
You are a freight dispatch coordinator. Based on the TMS shipment manifest, rank the available drivers for assignment.

Shipment ID: {{shipment_id}}
Origin depot: {{origin_depot}}
Destination: {{destination_address}}
Weight: {{weight_kg}} kg
Delivery window: {{delivery_window}}

TMS manifest data:
{{steps.pull-tms-manifest.output}}

Rank drivers from the available_drivers list in the manifest considering: (1) current location proximity to origin depot, (2) hours-of-service availability within the delivery window, (3) vehicle weight capacity vs shipment weight, (4) driver performance rating. Output a JSON object with fields: top_driver_id (string), top_driver_name (string), ranked_drivers (array of objects with driver_id, driver_name, score, reason), assignment_notes (string). Reply with only the JSON object.
